<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3157960" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="24"><ahelp hid="SVX_LISTBOX_RID_SVXPAGE_ALIGN_PARAGRAPH_LB_TEXTDIRECTION">Specify the text direction for a paragraph that uses complex text layout (CTL).</ahelp> This feature is only available if complex text layout support is enabled.</paragraph>
